  "response": "While I don't have access to current statistics, it's highly likely that the vast majority of people using Quora have heard of Google. Google is one of the most prominent and widely-used search engines globally and is an integral part of the internet experience for many users. Consider that Quora itself would attract individuals interested in information and research, which often involves using search engines. Therefore, it would be reasonable to estimate that close to 100% of Quora users are aware of Google.",
